name: Peacock flower print make up bag
description:
Floral print make up bag in navy blue and turquoise with chartreuse and gold chunky ykk zip.

Original design Inspired by print and patterns of the fabulous art nouveau/art deco eras.

Hand printed onto natural oatmeal coloured linen, the back is plain linen and the lining is a navy cotton lining.

Interlined for extra support.

Ideal to store make up or organise small accessories and gadgets.

Dimensions: w,22x h,15 x d,7cm

name: Peacock Flower cushion in Mustard & Grey
description:
Brighten up the home with this unique art deco inspired cushion.

Original design Inspired by print and patterns of the fabulous art nouveau/art deco eras. 

Silkscreen printed by hand in the UK in bright mustard yellow & grey onto a natural oatmeal coloured heavy weight linen, the reverse is plain Linen.

Woven label in the side seam, zip closure at bottom, seams are overlocked with a professional finish and comes complete with 18" UK made feather cushion pad. 

Dimensions approximately: 43 x 43cm.

Wash care - Dry clean cover separately.

Shipping price for Worldwide includes duck feather cushion inner but if you'd prefer to buy the cover alone the shipping cost will be reduced, so I  will refund you the difference!

name: Bicycle Tea Towel in Navy
description:
Add a bit of fun to the kitchen with this bicycle print tea towel!
An original design inspired by a vintage print I found.

Hand screen printed in the UK onto 100% unbleached cotton and comes with a printed woven ribbon for hanging up.

Also available in Red.

Tea towels come beautifully tied in twine and wrapped in tissue.

Dimensions: W47cm x H78cm

Machine wash at 30 degrees 
Iron on reverse.
